    <h2>1. Overview</h2>
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy explains how the Arcanara Tarot Bot (‚Äúthe Bot‚Äù) handles, stores,
      and protects information related to your use of its features within Discord.
      The Bot aims to respect user privacy while maintaining the functionality of its readings.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Information Collected</h2>
    <p>
      The Bot does not collect personal information such as real names, emails, or locations.
      However, it may temporarily process limited data provided automatically by Discord,
      including:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your Discord username and ID (used to identify your readings).</li>
      <li>Messages sent to the Bot (used only for providing readings or commands).</li>
      <li>Server and channel IDs (used for message routing and context).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
    <p>
      The Bot does not maintain permanent databases or external data logs.
      Temporary information, such as your current intention or recent reading, is stored
      only in memory and is lost when the Bot restarts. No data is sold, shared, or used
      for analytics.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p>
      The Bot operates entirely within Discord and does not use cookies, trackers,
      or third-party analytics tools.
    </p>

